* 2013: [[Booka Shade]], [[Boys Noize]], [[Lexy & K-Paul]], [[M.A.N.D.Y.]], [[Monika Kruse]], [[Moonbootica]], [[Pan-Pot]], [[DJ Wankelmut]], [[Onur Özer]]
